info: Clearwater Analytics Holdings, Inc. develops and provides a SaaS solution for automated investment accounting, data management, and reporting. The company offers Clearwater, an automated data aggregation and reporting solution for investment portfolio data. It offers reporting tools, such as compliance policy monitoring, performance measurement, and risk analysis. The company serves corporations, insurers, investment managers, and institutions. Clearwater Analytics Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Boise, Idaho. It has additional offices in New York, New York; London and Edinburgh, United Kingdom; Noida, India; Paris, France; and Singapore.
